119
00:06:45,750 --> 00:06:46,610
Your Highness!

120
00:06:47,780 --> 00:06:49,640
I'm concerned about your safety.

121
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:52,480
Do as I said!

122
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:01,270
Yes.

123
00:07:29,630 --> 00:07:30,360
Who's there?

124
00:07:33,070 --> 00:07:34,600
So, the capital

125
00:07:35,350 --> 00:07:36,950
traps lonely souls like you.

126
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,720
You taste no flavor in food or drinks

127
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:40,320
