132
00:07:51,950 --> 00:07:52,610
Where is he?

133
00:07:52,950 --> 00:07:53,950
You came to beg him to undo

134
00:07:53,950 --> 00:07:55,310
the Soul-Cleansing Charm?

135
00:07:55,310 --> 00:07:56,190
Or

136
00:07:56,390 --> 00:07:57,630
you still can't accept

137
00:07:57,630 --> 00:07:58,480
that you've long been

138
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,720
my defeated foe,

139
00:07:59,950 --> 00:08:00,830
you failed to get what you want,

140
00:08:00,830 --> 00:08:02,490
and you're left with nothing,

141
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,720
so you came to make a futile attempt?

142
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:06,750
You live

143
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:08,430
in constant fear and paranoia,

144
00:08:08,430 --> 00:08:09,720
and your life is so dull.

145
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:11,240
There's nothing enviable about that.

146
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:13,320
The winner takes all, and the loser gets nothing.

147
00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:14,530
I am the winner.

148
00:08:15,430 --> 00:08:16,690
You've never even seen

149
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:19,600
the scenery here before.

150
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:23,530
I can come here whenever I want.

151
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:24,870
Who can stop me?

152
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:25,830
Su Yishui,

153
00:08:26,950 --> 00:08:27,630
it seems

154
00:08:27,650 --> 00:08:29,310
you've never beaten me so far.

155
00:08:29,870 --> 00:08:31,070
Stop daydreaming.

156
00:08:32,270 --> 00:08:33,000
I'm not interested

157
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,789
in competing with a sickly person.

158
00:08:34,789 --> 00:08:36,000
Look at you now.

159
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:39,059
I guess you don't have many days left.

160
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,030
With someone like Dun Tian,

161
00:08:41,030 --> 00:08:42,890
a powerful immortal, helping me,

162
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,510
I will naturally still be the one

163
00:08:44,510 --> 00:08:45,840
who takes all in the end.

164
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:46,800
Is that so?

165
00:08:47,790 --> 00:08:48,550
I heard you wanted

166
00:08:48,550 --> 00:08:50,350
to use my body to extend your life

167
00:08:50,390 --> 00:08:51,590
and marry Xue Ranran.

168
00:08:52,150 --> 00:08:53,270
Unfortunately, all your schemes

169
00:08:53,270 --> 00:08:54,470
amounted to nothing.

170
00:08:54,670 --> 00:08:56,440
So what if you have Dun Tian's help?

171
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,480
He couldn't even save

172
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:58,840
