173
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,670
You can't attain ascension or understand

174
00:09:00,670 --> 00:09:02,440
the true meaning of immortality,

175
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:03,150
of course you don't know

176
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:05,000
how to make everything start anew.

177
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:06,600
Make everything start anew?

178
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:08,720
How?

179
00:09:11,630 --> 00:09:12,690
Why bother asking?

180
00:09:13,270 --> 00:09:15,470
You'll enter this game sooner or later.

181
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:26,130
If you were to die right now,

182
00:09:26,690 --> 00:09:29,150
could you still make everything start anew?

183
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:40,210
Who's there?

184
00:10:07,670 --> 00:10:08,740
Dun Tian,

185
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,440
