186
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,600
Fine, that's your choice.

187
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:12,770
But what grudge do you have against me?

188
00:10:12,770 --> 00:10:14,830
Why did you attack me again and again?

189
00:10:28,150 --> 00:10:29,030
Su Yishui,

190
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:31,360
I am not your enemy.

191
00:10:31,670 --> 00:10:34,240
Everything I've done is to help you.

192
00:10:34,870 --> 00:10:35,630
Help me?

193
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:37,640
You are lurking

194
00:10:37,670 --> 00:10:39,240
in Prince Ping's residence and won't show up.

195
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:40,050
You deliberately made a plan

196
00:10:40,050 --> 00:10:41,920
to get the Spirit Spring into my heart.

197
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:42,790
And you launched a sneak attack on me,

198
00:10:42,790 --> 00:10:44,320
erased my memories, and disturbed my mind.

199
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:45,360
Is that how you help me?

200
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:46,600
I just want you to know

201
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,720
how one wrong step

202
00:10:48,750 --> 00:10:49,720
led to another,

203
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:51,720
