204
00:10:53,290 --> 00:10:54,170
Mu Qingge,

205
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:55,840
I will spend my whole life seeking revenge!

206
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:57,120
Su Yu, Prince Ping,

207
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:59,890
and everyone who plotted against me must die!

208
00:11:04,030 --> 00:11:05,160
You're all the same!

209
00:11:05,340 --> 00:11:06,470
You all betrayed me!

210
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,240
Mu Qingge,

211
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:10,650
I will definitely kill you!

212
00:11:13,390 --> 00:11:15,670
Even if you torture me to death,

213
00:11:15,940 --> 00:11:18,700
when Prince Ping reigns over the universe

214
00:11:19,030 --> 00:11:21,510
and wipes out Prince Zong's men,

215
00:11:22,510 --> 00:11:24,630
