216
00:11:27,630 --> 00:11:28,360
Xiaoxiao?

217
00:11:28,870 --> 00:11:29,480
Yes.

218
00:11:29,630 --> 00:11:30,320
It's her.

219
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,750
Back then, the Prince Zong's residence

220
00:11:31,750 --> 00:11:33,750
spread news of Su Xiaoxiao's death.

221
