222
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:37,840
and suffered all kinds of humiliation.

223
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:39,840
She was originally unyielding even in the face of death.

224
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:40,790
Guess why

225
00:11:40,790 --> 00:11:42,670
she later became disheartened

226
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:44,640
and lived like a walking corpse.

227
00:11:45,260 --> 00:11:46,200
Ever since she knew

228
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:47,750
you gave up on claiming the throne,

229
00:11:47,750 --> 00:11:49,030
she had been like that.

230
00:11:49,790 --> 00:11:52,550
Poor girl. It was wrong for her to trust you back then.

231
00:11:52,550 --> 00:11:53,630
She and you

232
00:11:53,750 --> 00:11:56,030
shouldn't have ended up like this.

233
00:12:08,430 --> 00:12:10,190
The dragon scale foretells the future.

234
00:12:10,190 --> 00:12:11,390
This was the destiny you were

235
00:12:11,390 --> 00:12:13,050
meant to fulfill 19 years ago —

236
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:14,370
ruling the universe

237
00:12:14,390 --> 00:12:15,850
with unparalleled power.

238
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:17,640
If Mu Qingge hadn't intervened

239
00:12:17,640 --> 00:12:19,970
and forcibly changed everything,

240
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:22,790
you would have already fulfilled your wish.

241
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:25,510
I've brought you back to the beginning.

242
00:12:25,510 --> 00:12:26,960
This will once again become

243
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:28,360
