245
00:12:30,480 --> 00:12:32,320
You will be there no matter what.

246
00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:34,250
Then what about you?

247
00:12:34,520 --> 00:12:36,450
What role do you play in all of this?

248
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:46,790
I'm merely a guide.

249
00:12:47,320 --> 00:12:48,440
If my reigning over the universe

250
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:49,640
is the final outcome,

251
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:51,740
why is Su Yu so certain

252
00:12:51,740 --> 00:12:53,470
that he will get the last laugh?

253
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:55,010
Isn't that contradictory?

254
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:56,680
It can only prove that

255
00:12:57,030 --> 00:12:57,750
both I

256
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:58,840
and Su Yu

257
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:00,360
are merely pawns for you to fulfill

258
00:13:00,360 --> 00:13:01,200
your wish.

259
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,850
