260
00:13:05,500 --> 00:13:06,720
is just to bring your wife and daughters

261
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:07,790
back to your side.

262
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:12,670
Clever.

263
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:14,120
It seems

264
00:13:14,910 --> 00:13:15,840
you've guessed

265
00:13:15,870 --> 00:13:16,930
part of the answer.

266
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:18,910
However,

267
00:13:19,550 --> 00:13:21,510
while fulfilling my wish,

268
00:13:22,510 --> 00:13:23,320
we can also fulfill

269
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:24,780
the wishes of many others.

270
00:13:25,360 --> 00:13:26,360
We can achieve

271
00:13:26,910 --> 00:13:28,110
a win-win situation.

272
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:31,390
I'm all ears.

273
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:33,330
Don't be impatient.

274
00:13:33,390 --> 00:13:34,590
It's not the time yet.

275
00:13:36,260 --> 00:13:37,240
You're being cagey.

276
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:38,960
So much for the win-win situation.

277
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:40,410
Do you expect me to be like Su Yu,

278
00:13:40,410 --> 00:13:41,610
relying on you to live

279
00:13:41,630 --> 00:13:42,490
