280
00:13:42,550 --> 00:13:44,150
and obeying all your orders?

281
00:13:44,860 --> 00:13:46,090
I won't let anyone else

282
00:13:46,090 --> 00:13:47,060
control my fate.

283
00:13:47,740 --> 00:13:48,600
I'm actually interested

284
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:49,790
in fighting against you to the end.

285
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:51,650
I will never let you have your way!

286
00:13:59,440 --> 00:14:00,390
Interesting.

287
00:14:02,630 --> 00:14:03,360
Su Yu,

288
00:14:04,270 --> 00:14:05,240
