When the demonic creature attacked,

292
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:37,220
I could have dodged it.

293
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:38,270
But you

294
00:14:38,300 --> 00:14:39,960
just used your hand to stop it.

295
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:42,030
Ms. Wen.

296
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:43,200
Elder Yan.

297
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:44,960
Ranran,

298
00:14:45,240 --> 00:14:46,300
let's sit and talk.

299
00:14:49,750 --> 00:14:50,960
I saw Hollow Sect's signal talisman

300
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:51,870
nearby,

301
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:53,050
so I rushed here.

302
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:54,030
On my way here,

303
00:14:54,240 --> 00:14:55,770
I killed a devilized demon.

304
00:14:56,510 --> 00:14:57,670
Just now, we eliminated

305
00:14:57,670 --> 00:14:59,630
a group of devilized demons nearby.

306
00:14:59,630 --> 00:15:00,960
You must have encountered one

307
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:01,870
that escaped.

308
00:15:01,960 --> 00:15:02,750
Currently,

309
00:15:02,750 --> 00:15:04,870
the devilization of demons is getting worse.

310
00:15:04,870 --> 00:15:06,330
We must solve the problem.

311
00:15:06,790 --> 00:15:08,080
Based on the current information

312
00:15:08,080 --> 00:15:09,120
gathered from various sources,

313
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:10,630
only the Gold Refining Fire

314
00:15:10,630 --> 00:15:12,750
can thoroughly purify the energy in the universe

315
00:15:12,750 --> 00:15:13,790
and handle the devilization.

316
00:15:13,790 --> 00:15:15,120
The Gold Refining Fire?

317
00:15:16,760 --> 00:15:18,230
It's said that the Spirit Spring,

318
00:15:18,230 --> 00:15:19,630
transformed from Mortal-Demon Lord's spiritual power,

319
00:15:19,630 --> 00:15:21,210
was sealed in the netherworld,

320
00:15:21,210 --> 00:15:23,320
but his remains remained indestructible.

321
00:15:23,320 --> 00:15:24,240
The immortals then

322
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:25,970
created the Gold Refining Fire

323
00:15:26,030 --> 00:15:27,910
to burn Mortal-Demon Lord's remains to ashes.

324
00:15:27,910 --> 00:15:28,790
Is that it?

325
00:15:30,150 --> 00:15:31,790
Mortal-Demon Lord's remains were sealed

326
00:15:31,790 --> 00:15:32,910
at the former site of Celestial Sect:

327
00:15:32,910 --> 00:15:34,110
Mount Scarlet Flame.

328
00:15:34,480 --> 00:15:35,510
Mount Scarlet Flame

329
00:15:35,510 --> 00:15:37,370
is currently occupied by Wei Jiu.

330
00:15:37,810 --> 00:15:38,910
Tu Jiuyuan, his subordinate,

331
00:15:38,910 --> 00:15:40,270
is willing to cooperate with us

332
00:15:40,270 --> 00:15:41,870
to obtain the Gold Refining Fire together.

333
00:15:41,870 --> 00:15:42,530
Therefore,

334
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:43,810
I have sent a message

335
00:15:43,810 --> 00:15:45,080
to all the Heavenly Sects,

336
00:15:45,080 --> 00:15:47,030
inviting them to go to Mount Scarlet Flame together

337
00:15:47,030 --> 00:15:48,390
to break the formation and obtain the fire.

338
00:15:48,390 --> 00:15:49,790
But what Tu Jiuyuan wants

339
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:51,930
might not be what Wei Jiu wants.

340
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:54,120
Of course we should be wary in case it's a trap.

341
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:55,240
If we can obtain it peacefully, that's fine.

342
00:15:55,240 --> 00:15:56,000
If not,

343
00:15:56,510 --> 00:15:57,770
we'll take it by force.

344
00:16:01,910 --> 00:16:02,630
Ranran,

345
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:04,320
Yishui has always been unwilling

346
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:06,780
to associate with the other Heavenly Sects.

347
00:16:06,990 --> 00:16:08,320
I wonder if Wester Sect

348
00:16:09,200 --> 00:16:10,960
is willing to go with us this time.

349
00:16:10,960 --> 00:16:13,000
No matter what Master's decision is,

350
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:13,870
I, Xue Ranran,

351
00:16:14,150 --> 00:16:15,840
will definitely do what I can

352
00:16:16,070 --> 00:16:18,330
to help solve the devilization problem.

353
00:16:19,630 --> 00:16:21,430
Who are you sending a message to?

354
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:25,240
Who is it for?

355
00:16:25,790 --> 00:16:27,200
What's the message about?

356
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:28,550
I told Master

357
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:31,730
you plan to secretly go to Mount Scarlet Flame

358
00:16:31,730 --> 00:16:33,200
to get the Gold Refining Fire.

359
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:33,670
You...

360
00:16:34,850 --> 00:16:35,910
All you care about now

361
00:16:35,910 --> 00:16:37,150
is your master.

362
00:16:37,510 --> 00:16:39,370
Your heart is with her too, right?

363
00:16:40,150 --> 00:16:41,550
Where does that leave me?

364
00:16:43,630 --> 00:16:44,440
Wu,

365
00:16:44,840 --> 00:16:46,100
I'm doing this for you.

366
00:16:46,700 --> 00:16:47,960
Right now, all the Heavenly Sects

367
00:16:47,960 --> 00:16:49,960
are heading to Mount Scarlet Flame.

368
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:51,240
Master will definitely go too

369
00:16:51,240 --> 00:16:53,100
to obtain the Gold Refining Fire.

370
00:16:53,270 --> 00:16:54,670
You're no match for them.

371
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:57,000
I revealed your plan

372
00:16:58,030 --> 00:16:59,960
because I want you to give up.

373
00:17:00,750 --> 00:17:02,200
Why do you have to risk your life

374
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:03,600
for Dun Tian?

375
00:17:04,430 --> 00:17:06,030
You don't understand at all.

376
00:17:06,599 --> 00:17:07,400
I understand.

377
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:11,060
When you were drunk that day, you said

378
00:17:11,480 --> 00:17:12,310
Dun Tian would take you

379
00:17:12,310 --> 00:17:13,589
to another world —

380
00:17:14,480 --> 00:17:15,920
a world without Qingge.

381
00:17:17,240 --> 00:17:18,310
I just want to know

382
00:17:18,750 --> 00:17:20,280
if you can give me what I want

383
00:17:20,550 --> 00:17:22,310
after all that I've done.

384
00:17:24,750 --> 00:17:25,440
Wu,

385
00:17:26,270 --> 00:17:27,829
I remember you once said

386
00:17:28,590 --> 00:17:29,480
if Mu Qingge didn't exist

387
00:17:29,480 --> 00:17:30,510
in this world,

388
00:17:31,030 --> 00:17:32,790
you might live more at ease.

389
00:17:33,640 --> 00:17:34,270
What if there really is

390
00:17:34,270 --> 00:17:35,550
a world like that?

391
00:17:35,960 --> 00:17:37,110
From beginning to end,

392
00:17:37,110 --> 00:17:38,750
you would be the only daughter in your family.

393
00:17:38,750 --> 00:17:41,080
You wouldn't need to compete with others.

394
00:17:41,170 --> 00:17:42,560
Would you be happy?

395
00:17:45,160 --> 00:17:46,750
You still don't understand.

396
00:17:46,750 --> 00:17:48,350
Uncle Ye Xin just told me

397
00:17:48,350 --> 00:17:49,810
that there is such a world.

398
00:17:51,160 --> 00:17:52,240
He never said

399
00:17:52,240 --> 00:17:53,500
he would take me there.

400
00:17:54,310 --> 00:17:55,750
Because in his eyes,

401
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:58,480
I'm not important at all.

402
00:18:00,790 --> 00:18:02,240
So I have to get

403
00:18:02,640 --> 00:18:04,370
more useful bargaining chips.

404
00:18:04,680 --> 00:18:06,480
He wants the Gold Refining Fire,

405
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:07,750
then I have to get

406
00:18:07,750 --> 00:18:09,080
the Gold Refining Fire.

407
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:11,680
That way,

408
00:18:13,550 --> 00:18:14,750
I can bargain with Uncle Ye Xin

409
00:18:14,750 --> 00:18:15,920
about the next step.

410
00:18:19,060 --> 00:18:20,190
No one can stop me

411
00:18:22,740 --> 00:18:24,140
from getting what I want.

412
00:18:29,760 --> 00:18:30,820
This way, this way.

413
00:18:32,910 --> 00:18:34,540
It was really good tonight.

414
00:18:35,550 --> 00:18:36,080
Goodbye.

415
00:18:37,450 --> 00:18:38,380
I'll come again.

416
00:18:38,500 --> 00:18:39,020
Okay.

417
00:18:40,760 --> 00:18:43,470
When Prince Ping reigns over the universe,

418
00:18:43,530 --> 00:18:46,000
you'll get what you deserve.

419
00:18:47,200 --> 00:18:48,200
Get her out

420
00:18:48,680 --> 00:18:50,080
and take good care of her.

421
00:18:50,530 --> 00:18:51,010
Yes.

422
00:19:17,530 --> 00:19:18,120
Master.

423
00:19:18,840 --> 00:19:20,080
Since everything was fine,

424
00:19:20,080 --> 00:19:21,610
why were you sleeping here?

425
00:19:21,770 --> 00:19:23,500
I heard you went to the capital.

426
00:19:23,530 --> 00:19:24,360
I was worried.

427
00:19:24,570 --> 00:19:25,700
Worried about Su Yu?

428
00:19:27,120 --> 00:19:28,010
Were you worried I would

429
00:19:28,010 --> 00:19:29,050
kill him and his whole family

430
00:19:29,050 --> 00:19:30,360
and just take his place?

431
00:19:30,360 --> 00:19:30,880
Is he...

432
00:19:31,330 --> 00:19:32,050
alright?

433
00:19:33,640 --> 00:19:35,500
You really are worried about him.

434
00:19:36,400 --> 00:19:38,570
I heard you used to live in the imperial palace

435
00:19:38,570 --> 00:19:40,430
and you were around him every day.

436
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:42,370
And he even wanted to marry you.

437
00:19:45,460 --> 00:19:46,770
How did you manage to flirt with him

438
00:19:46,770 --> 00:19:48,100
while also seducing me?

439
00:19:53,880 --> 00:19:55,390
Who is he to be compared to me?

440
00:19:55,390 --> 00:19:56,380
I'm going to kill him right now!

441
00:19:56,380 --> 00:19:57,400
From beginning to end,

442
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:58,810
you've always been the one I like.

443
00:19:58,810 --> 00:20:00,140
I was worried about you.

444
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:05,330
Worried about what?

445
00:20:06,090 --> 00:20:06,840
Do you think I would let

446
00:20:06,840 --> 00:20:08,970
Dun Tian, that old man, manipulate me?

447
00:20:10,530 --> 00:20:12,530
I don't know what Dun Tian's plan is,

448
00:20:12,670 --> 00:20:13,570
but since he desperately wants me

449
00:20:13,570 --> 00:20:14,970
to send an army and create chaos,

450
00:20:14,970 --> 00:20:17,300
I'll do just the opposite of what he wants.

451
00:20:17,700 --> 00:20:18,370
Master,

452
00:20:18,600 --> 00:20:19,860
you're not going to send an army?

453
00:20:19,860 --> 00:20:21,010
I've just decided to postpone the plan

454
00:20:21,010 --> 00:20:22,640
based on the current situation.

455
00:20:22,640 --> 00:20:23,250
Don't think

456
00:20:23,250 --> 00:20:25,050
you've influenced me in any way.

457
00:20:27,840 --> 00:20:29,250
Master, you're wise and strong,

458
00:20:29,250 --> 00:20:30,290
resourceful and reasonable,

459
00:20:30,290 --> 00:20:31,090
and resolute.

460
00:20:39,490 --> 00:20:40,090
By the way,

461
00:20:40,490 --> 00:20:42,200
to solve the devilization problem,

462
00:20:42,200 --> 00:20:44,200
the other Heavenly Sects plan to go to Celestial Sect's Mount Scarlet Flame

463
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:45,640
to obtain the Gold Refining Fire.

464
00:20:45,640 --> 00:20:47,770
Master, would you like to go together?

465
00:20:47,770 --> 00:20:49,250
Since the devilization problem is somehow

466
00:20:49,250 --> 00:20:50,490
related to Dun Tian,

467
00:20:51,120 --> 00:20:51,810
and he prompted the Heavenly Sects

468
00:20:51,810 --> 00:20:53,470
to get the Gold Refining Fire,

469
00:20:53,530 --> 00:20:54,990
he must be up to something.

470
00:20:55,330 --> 00:20:55,920
Mu...

471
00:20:56,920 --> 00:20:57,880
Mu Qingge

472
00:20:58,120 --> 00:21:00,820
is also determined to obtain the Gold Refining Fire.

473
00:21:00,820 --> 00:21:01,570
Maybe Dun Tian

474
00:21:01,570 --> 00:21:03,330
wants to use the Heavenly Sects

475
00:21:03,360 --> 00:21:04,620
to break the formation and obtain the fire,

476
00:21:04,620 --> 00:21:06,080
and then take it from them.

477
00:21:06,160 --> 00:21:07,890
Something doesn't feel right.

478
00:21:08,010 --> 00:21:09,290
But with demonic creatures running rampant,

479
00:21:09,290 --> 00:21:10,490
the world is in chaos.

480
00:21:11,010 --> 00:21:12,740
No matter what Dun Tian is up to,

481
00:21:12,770 --> 00:21:14,290
we can only be cautious

482
00:21:14,840 --> 00:21:16,290
and obtain the Gold Refining Fire

483
00:21:16,290 --> 00:21:18,250
to eliminate devils and restore order.

484
00:21:18,250 --> 00:21:20,580
Indeed, we can't let Dun Tian have his way.

485
00:21:20,770 --> 00:21:22,500
I'll get the Gold Refining Fire

486
00:21:22,530 --> 00:21:23,730
and see what he'll do.

487
00:21:23,980 --> 00:21:24,650
Master,

488
00:21:24,970 --> 00:21:26,700
you're willing to go together?

489
00:21:26,970 --> 00:21:28,930
I heard that a demonic cultivator named Wei Jiu

490
00:21:28,930 --> 00:21:30,050
has been boasting a name on par with mine

491
00:21:30,050 --> 00:21:31,440
to deceive people across the universe

492
00:21:31,440 --> 00:21:32,680
over the past ten-odd years.

493
00:21:32,680 --> 00:21:34,040
I'd like to meet him.

494
00:21:36,050 --> 00:21:36,570
Right,

495
00:21:37,040 --> 00:21:38,570
Wang Suizhi, who sent me the message,

496
00:21:38,570 --> 00:21:40,370
also mentioned something else.

497
00:21:40,490 --> 00:21:41,440
He said

498
00:21:41,640 --> 00:21:42,360
Dun Tian

499
00:21:42,380 --> 00:21:43,840
mentioned another world.

500
00:21:45,050 --> 00:21:46,090
The Spirit Spring.

501
00:21:46,090 --> 00:21:47,420
The Gold Refining Fire.

502
00:21:47,600 --> 00:21:48,840
Make everything start anew.

503
00:21:48,840 --> 00:21:49,970
Another world.

504
00:21:51,120 --> 00:21:53,050
What on earth is their connection?

505
00:21:57,610 --> 00:21:58,440
Sovereign,

506
00:21:58,570 --> 00:22:00,050
you only asked us to keep an eye on Elder Tu

507
00:22:00,050 --> 00:22:01,640
to prevent her from recklessly entering the formation

508
00:22:01,640 --> 00:22:03,050
or suddenly leaving the sect.

509
00:22:03,050 --> 00:22:04,600
But I...

510
00:22:04,810 --> 00:22:05,970
saw something else.

511
00:22:06,640 --> 00:22:08,330
I'm not sure if I should report it to you.

512
00:22:08,330 --> 00:22:09,200
What is it exactly?

513
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:10,400
What happened to her?

514
00:22:12,440 --> 00:22:13,330
Just tell me!

515
00:22:13,890 --> 00:22:14,880
Elder Tu sent a secret message

516
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:15,820
to the Heavenly Sects,

517
00:22:15,820 --> 00:22:16,570
inviting them to come

518
00:22:16,570 --> 00:22:17,970
to Celestial Sect's Mount Scarlet Flame

519
00:22:17,970 --> 00:22:19,530
to obtain the Gold Refining Fire.

520
00:22:19,530 --> 00:22:20,390
How dare she...

521
00:22:23,040 --> 00:22:25,300
Does she really want to leave that badly?

522
00:22:37,270 --> 00:22:39,840
Anyway, with the power of Celestial Sect alone,

523
00:22:39,840 --> 00:22:40,640
it would be difficult

524
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:42,660
to break the Five Deadly Formations in a short time.

525
00:22:42,660 --> 00:22:43,730
Since those Heavenly Sects' men

526
00:22:43,730 --> 00:22:44,930
have been lured here,

527
00:22:45,570 --> 00:22:46,770
why don't I set up a formation

528
00:22:46,770 --> 00:22:47,460
in the back mountain

529
00:22:47,460 --> 00:22:48,390
to welcome them?

530
00:22:49,320 --> 00:22:51,180
After they break the formations,

531
00:22:51,200 --> 00:22:52,890
I'll take advantage of that

532
00:22:53,010 --> 00:22:54,670
to get the Gold Refining Fire.

533
00:22:55,120 --> 00:22:57,050
Sovereign, that's a brilliant strategy.

534
00:22:57,050 --> 00:22:58,160
Then Elder Tu...

535
00:22:58,600 --> 00:22:59,660
Don't let her know.

536
00:23:00,070 --> 00:23:00,490
I

537
00:23:00,490 --> 00:23:01,330
intend to catch her

538
00:23:01,330 --> 00:23:02,250
off guard.

539
00:23:03,400 --> 00:23:04,440
As long as the Gold Refining Fire

540
00:23:04,440 --> 00:23:06,250
isn't given to me by her personally,

541
00:23:06,250 --> 00:23:08,400
it can't be considered that she has fulfilled her promise.

542
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:10,240
[Mount Wester]

543
00:23:12,520 --> 00:23:13,650
This time,

544
00:23:13,680 --> 00:23:14,850
I can finally ride

545
00:23:14,870 --> 00:23:15,970
the luxurious carriage

546
00:23:15,970 --> 00:23:17,630
I didn't get to ride last time.

547
00:23:18,320 --> 00:23:19,120
The other disciples

548
00:23:19,120 --> 00:23:20,770
are on their way there by riding a sword.

549
00:23:20,770 --> 00:23:22,900
You guys go there by riding a sword too.

550
00:23:24,440 --> 00:23:24,840
You,

551
00:23:24,920 --> 00:23:26,050
get in the carriage.

552
00:23:28,200 --> 00:23:29,800
-Yes, Master.
-Yes, Master.

553
00:23:32,880 --> 00:23:34,010
The carriage...

554
00:23:34,190 --> 00:23:35,340
is for me?

555
00:23:37,600 --> 00:23:38,920
Your spiritual power is so weak,

556
00:23:38,920 --> 00:23:40,170
and you can't ride a sword.

557
00:23:40,170 --> 00:23:42,100
Do you expect me to carry you there?

558
00:23:42,810 --> 00:23:44,670
I'll just ride the carriage then.

559
00:23:55,050 --> 00:23:55,770
Mu Qingge?

560
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:57,970
What are you doing here?

561
00:23:58,540 --> 00:23:59,770
Back then, you slandered Su Yishui by saying

562
00:23:59,770 --> 00:24:00,710
he was going to turn into a devil.

563
00:24:00,710 --> 00:24:02,570
It almost delayed the sealing of the Spirit Spring.

564
00:24:02,570 --> 00:24:03,330
This time,

565
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:04,770
what are you up to?

566
00:24:05,160 --> 00:24:07,250
Immortal Master Wen, your words are too harsh.

567
00:24:07,250 --> 00:24:08,710
I was misinformed before,

568
00:24:09,160 --> 00:24:10,760
and I'm truly sorry for that.

569
00:24:10,910 --> 00:24:12,080
So I came here

570
00:24:12,300 --> 00:24:13,500
to help obtain

571
00:24:13,530 --> 00:24:14,790
the Gold Refining Fire

572
00:24:14,920 --> 00:24:16,250
to make amends for that.

573
00:24:16,360 --> 00:24:17,120
Since you're willing

574
00:24:17,120 --> 00:24:18,840
to join us in obtaining the Gold Refining Fire

575
00:24:18,840 --> 00:24:21,050
to suppress demonic creatures and benefit the people,

576
00:24:21,050 --> 00:24:22,510
we naturally welcome you.

577
00:24:23,330 --> 00:24:25,050
