00:36:00,410 --> 00:36:01,850
Her malicious energy is so strong.

861
00:36:01,850 --> 00:36:02,800
I don't think she's one of the five guardians

862
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:03,600
protecting the formations.

863
00:36:03,600 --> 00:36:05,060
They don't have children.

864
00:36:05,160 --> 00:36:06,050
The song?

865
00:36:06,530 --> 00:36:07,370
Little girls?

866
00:36:07,850 --> 00:36:08,720
She's Rong Yao!

867
00:36:09,010 --> 00:36:10,750
Back in the Memory Cave at the Heavenly Meridian Mountain,

868
00:36:10,750 --> 00:36:12,360
I saw Dun Tian's memories.

869
00:36:12,600 --> 00:36:14,620
The tune his wife, Rong Yao, was humming

870
00:36:14,620 --> 00:36:16,280
is exactly what we just heard!

871
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:19,240
Rong Yao has taken control of the formations.

872
00:36:19,240 --> 00:36:20,010
What?

873
00:36:20,500 --> 00:36:21,570
Dun Tian's wife

874
00:36:21,800 --> 00:36:24,010
can actually contaminate the formations with malicious energy?

875
00:36:24,010 --> 00:36:25,570
Back then, in order to attain enlightenment, Dun Tian

876
00:36:25,570 --> 00:36:26,760
chose to sacrifice his wife and daughters,

877
00:36:26,760 --> 00:36:28,090
while he himself attained ascension.

878
00:36:28,090 --> 00:36:29,490
Rong Yao and their daughters

879
00:36:29,490 --> 00:36:31,290
were abandoned and sacrificed.

880
00:36:31,640 --> 00:36:32,570
Of course she had

881
00:36:32,690 --> 00:36:33,410
strong resentment.

882
00:36:33,410 --> 00:36:34,010
No wonder.

883
00:36:34,640 --> 00:36:35,720
Although Rong Yao is dead,

884
00:36:35,720 --> 00:36:37,720
her resentment hasn't disappeared over the past few hundred years.

885
00:36:37,720 --> 00:36:40,450
And her malicious energy has gradually contaminated the formations.

886
00:36:40,450 --> 00:36:41,490
It seems Dun Tian is not the only one

887
00:36:41,490 --> 00:36:42,550
who can't let it go.

888
00:36:42,640 --> 00:36:44,090
Rong Yao can't let it go either.

889
00:36:44,090 --> 00:36:45,450
Why did you break in?

890
00:36:46,090 --> 00:36:47,930
All of you deserve to die!

891
00:36:48,410 --> 00:36:49,530
Kill!

892
00:36:53,170 --> 00:36:54,760
Fighting the malicious energy is useless!

893
00:36:54,760 --> 00:36:55,890
Rong Yao is the eye of the formation!

894
00:36:55,890 --> 00:36:56,930
We need to break her true form

895
00:36:56,930 --> 00:36:57,680
to escape!

896
00:36:57,930 --> 00:36:58,490
Master,

897
00:36:58,640 --> 00:36:59,500
let me help you.

898
00:37:01,570 --> 00:37:02,300
Divine Tree!

899
00:37:15,320 --> 00:37:16,380
-Master!
-Master!

900
00:37:19,050 --> 00:37:21,980
You actually managed to hurt me by working together.

901
00:37:22,120 --> 00:37:23,800
I underestimated you.

902
00:37:24,370 --> 00:37:25,320
Your behavior of risking

903
00:37:25,320 --> 00:37:27,120
your lives to protect each other

904
00:37:27,120 --> 00:37:28,850
has really irritated me!

905
00:37:29,580 --> 00:37:31,690
You should know that love

906
00:37:31,720 --> 00:37:32,840
is the most hypocritical

907
00:37:32,840 --> 00:37:34,500
and unreliable in this world!

908
00:37:34,600 --> 00:37:36,530
Today, let me see

909
00:37:37,450 --> 00:37:39,250
how long your hypocritical love

910
00:37:39,280 --> 00:37:40,640
can last!

911
00:37:56,270 --> 00:37:57,630
What did you do to us?

912
00:37:57,800 --> 00:37:59,590
What I cast on you

913
00:37:59,980 --> 00:38:02,680
is Celestial Sect's most powerful torture spell:

914
00:38:02,680 --> 00:38:04,140
the Lone Star Blood Spell!

915
00:38:05,360 --> 00:38:06,640
Those under the spell will endure

916
00:38:06,640 --> 00:38:08,770
searing pain as if consumed by flames.

917
00:38:09,410 --> 00:38:10,890
The stronger one's spiritual power is,

918
00:38:10,890 --> 00:38:13,050
the greater pain that person will suffer.

919
00:38:13,050 --> 00:38:15,240
The blood spell won't end

920
00:38:16,090 --> 00:38:17,890
until either of you dies.

921
00:38:20,980 --> 00:38:21,690
The spell

922
00:38:21,720 --> 00:38:23,780
has connected your spiritual power.

923
00:38:23,800 --> 00:38:24,680
If you transfer

924
00:38:24,720 --> 00:38:26,200
your spiritual power to the other person,

925
00:38:26,200 --> 00:38:27,760
you'll suffer less pain.

926
00:38:28,220 --> 00:38:29,270
How are you feeling?

927
00:38:29,270 --> 00:38:30,470
It's painful, right?

928
00:38:32,810 --> 00:38:33,610
Then transfer

929
00:38:33,640 --> 00:38:35,280
your spiritual power to the other person!

930
00:38:35,280 --> 00:38:37,010
As long as you betray the other,

931
00:38:37,640 --> 00:38:39,640
you can survive!

932
00:38:43,560 --> 00:38:45,890
I'd like to see how much longer you can hold on!

933
00:38:45,890 --> 00:38:46,760
Invoke!

934
00:38:52,160 --> 00:38:52,620
Ranran!

935
00:38:52,760 --> 00:38:53,240
Master!

936
00:39:01,010 --> 00:39:02,470
The Soul-Devouring Lock.

937
00:39:09,200 --> 00:39:10,010
Mu Ranwu and Ranran

938
00:39:10,010 --> 00:39:11,280
are connected by the Soul-Devouring Lock.

939
00:39:11,280 --> 00:39:12,550
They share each other's spiritual power,

940
00:39:12,550 --> 00:39:13,370
so Mu Ranwu is also under the spell

941
00:39:13,370 --> 00:39:14,970
and has been dragged into it!

942
00:39:17,280 --> 00:39:19,280
Master and the others are in danger!

943
00:39:20,570 --> 00:39:22,300
You can't break free from this.

944
00:39:22,640 --> 00:39:24,040
The Lone Star Blood Spell

945
00:39:24,200 --> 00:39:25,890
won't kill all of you.

946
00:39:26,600 --> 00:39:27,600
You have plenty of ways

947
00:39:27,600 --> 00:39:29,320
to ensure your own survival.

948
00:39:29,850 --> 00:39:30,760
What do you think?

949
00:39:30,760 --> 00:39:32,160
Isn't this interesting?

950
00:39:33,890 --> 00:39:34,720
You two

951
00:39:35,090 --> 00:39:36,720
are this monster's target!

952
00:39:37,090 --> 00:39:38,640
Why should I suffer

953
00:39:39,200 --> 00:39:40,090
all this with you

954
00:39:40,090 --> 00:39:41,320
even at this point?

955
00:39:46,370 --> 00:39:48,320
Xue Ranran's spiritual power is weak now.

956
00:39:48,320 --> 00:39:50,490
All the pain and pressure are on my side.

957
00:39:50,490 --> 00:39:51,550
If this continues,

958
00:39:51,930 --> 00:39:54,330
I definitely won't be able to withstand it.

959
00:40:05,680 --> 00:40:06,570
Xue Ranran!

960
00:40:07,760 --> 00:40:09,530
I don't want any of this anymore!

961
00:40:09,530 --> 00:40:11,130
I'm giving it all back to you!

962
00:40:11,410 --> 00:40:12,680
I'm giving all the spiritual power

963
00:40:12,680 --> 00:40:13,760
back to you!

964
00:40:13,850 --> 00:40:16,110
Xue Ranran, I'm giving it all back to you!

965
00:40:23,760 --> 00:40:24,320
Ranran!

966
00:40:24,590 --> 00:40:26,590
The Soul-Devouring Lock is broken!

967
00:40:31,090 --> 00:40:31,850
Oh no.

968
00:40:31,890 --> 00:40:33,240
Since the Soul-Devouring Lock is broken,

969
00:40:33,240 --> 00:40:35,090
all the spiritual power has returned to Ranran's body.

970
00:40:35,090 --> 00:40:36,350
These blood chains...

971
00:40:36,720 --> 00:40:37,760
The stronger Ranran's spiritual power is,

972
00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:39,620
the greater pain she will suffer!

973
00:40:44,720 --> 00:40:45,370
Give it to me!

974
00:40:45,370 --> 00:40:46,100
This is mine!

975
00:40:46,120 --> 00:40:47,280
Don't hit my sister!

976
00:40:51,570 --> 00:40:52,900
This is my Mount Wester.

977
00:40:54,230 --> 00:40:55,000
Shui,

978
00:40:55,850 --> 00:40:56,600
it's you.

979
00:41:40,020 --> 00:41:40,640
Shui?

980
00:41:50,300 --> 00:41:52,320
I've regained all my spiritual power

981
00:41:52,320 --> 00:41:53,920
at the Transcendence Stage.

982
00:41:56,570 --> 00:41:57,800
If you want to live,

983
00:41:58,600 --> 00:41:59,600
just transfer your spiritual power

984
00:41:59,600 --> 00:42:00,800
to the other person!

985
00:42:01,850 --> 00:42:03,450
Today, let me see which of you

986
00:42:04,370 --> 00:42:06,120
can win and which of you

987
00:42:10,010 --> 00:42:11,850
will die first!

988
00:42:14,450 --> 00:42:15,490
Sword of Non-Attachment!

989
00:42:15,490 --> 00:42:17,020
Focus and gather the power.

990
00:42:17,760 --> 00:42:19,410
Harness the energy to command the spirits!

991
00:42:19,410 --> 00:42:20,200
Converge!

992
00:42:22,720 --> 00:42:23,780
What are you doing?

993
00:42:23,810 --> 00:42:24,800
Temporarily boosting

994
00:42:24,800 --> 00:42:26,280
your spiritual power through the living creatures

995
00:42:26,280 --> 00:42:28,410
will make the blood chains rush towards you!

996
00:42:28,410 --> 00:42:30,120
You won't be able to withstand it!

997
00:42:30,120 --> 00:42:30,850
Cut the crap!

998
00:42:32,160 --> 00:42:33,820
I'm not doing this to save you.

999
00:42:34,050 --> 00:42:35,570
I came here to break the formations

1000
00:42:35,570 --> 00:42:37,430
to obtain the Gold Refining Fire.

1001
00:42:37,760 --> 00:42:39,120
We can't all die here!

1002
00:42:44,890 --> 00:42:45,640
But you...

1003
00:42:48,970 --> 00:42:49,450
Ranran,

1004
00:42:50,200 --> 00:42:50,930
listen to me.

1005
00:42:51,850 --> 00:42:54,650
Rong Yao's malicious energy is truly formidable,

1006
00:42:56,050 --> 00:42:57,010
but she's used it all

1007
00:42:57,010 --> 00:42:58,670
on the blood chain formation.

1008
00:43:03,200 --> 00:43:04,450
Rong Yao herself

1009
00:43:05,010 --> 00:43:06,970
is now the most vulnerable.

1010
00:43:08,050 --> 00:43:08,970
Now,

1011
00:43:09,930 --> 00:43:12,060
I'm drawing the blood chains to myself

1012
00:43:12,120 --> 00:43:13,530
to reduce your pain.

1013
00:43:17,490 --> 00:43:19,160
You take this chance to gather your power

1014
00:43:19,160 --> 00:43:20,560
and attack Rong Yao directly!

1015
00:43:20,560 --> 00:43:21,890
We only have one chance.

1016
00:43:22,010 --> 00:43:23,570
You have to succeed!

1017
00:43:32,530 --> 00:43:33,530
-Master!
-Master!

